title: Doctor Who - The Dalek Invasion of Earth
description:
So far, Dalek Invasion of the Earth is one of the better Hartnell stories I've watched.

The crew of the TARDIS land in a post-apocalyptic London and have to deal with Earth's new dictators as well as the worst traits of humanity willing to do anything to survive; even betray one another.

Many interesting location shots outside the tiny Lime Grove studio, great new Dalek saucer sets, as well as new CGI shots in this serial.

This arc will form the basis of the Peter Cushing sequel movie, Daleks' Invasion Earth 2150 A.D.

Direct MKV rip from DVD source.
